# Binary assets are tracked with Git LFS (decision 2026-07-18) so heavyweight
# blobs never enter regular git history.
# NOTE: GitHub Pages' legacy branch build serves LFS *pointer files*, not the
# binaries — images on the published docs site resolve only once the Phase 5
# Actions-based site build (LFS-aware checkout) replaces it. GitHub's own
# markdown rendering of the repo is unaffected. See docs/development/TechStack.md.
*.png filter=lfs diff=lfs merge=lfs -text
*.jpg filter=lfs diff=lfs merge=lfs -text
*.jpeg filter=lfs diff=lfs merge=lfs -text
*.gif filter=lfs diff=lfs merge=lfs -text
*.webp filter=lfs diff=lfs merge=lfs -text
*.mp3 filter=lfs diff=lfs merge=lfs -text
*.wav filter=lfs diff=lfs merge=lfs -text
*.icns filter=lfs diff=lfs merge=lfs -text
*.ico filter=lfs diff=lfs merge=lfs -text
